headline: Why Fast-paced Mover Jabil (JBL) Is a Great Choice for Value Investors
summary: If you are looking for stocks that have gained strong momentum recently but are still trading at reasonable prices, Jabil (JBL) could be a great choice. It is one of the several stocks that passed through our 'Fast-Paced Momentum at a Bargain' screen.
